Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.47,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We've arrived.{NOTE:私たちが来た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.43,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,To America. To New York.{NOTE:アメリカへ。ニューヨークへ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:27.14,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,And at the World Junior Volleyball Championship.{NOTE:そして世界ジュニアバレーボール選手権大会へ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:31.29,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The long and painful training camp was all for this week.{NOTE:長く苦しかった特訓も全ては今日からの一週間に掛かっている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:19.96,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's right.{NOTE:そう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:25.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori's serve starts the battle we bet our youth on.{NOTE:みどりの打つこのサーブから儂達の青春を掛けた戦いが始まるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.65,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.74,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Cassie's smiling.{NOTE:キャシーが笑った。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:52.58,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Is that self-esteem of a team placed second last year?{NOTE:あれが去年準優勝したチームの貫禄かしら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:56.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Protect me, Dad.{NOTE:パパ、みどりを守って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She did it!{NOTE:やったわ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.35,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I did it.{NOTE:決まった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.64,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Somehow.{NOTE:何か助けないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Good!{NOTE:上手い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.58,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy.{NOTE:軽い軽い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:38.50,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Hayakawa-san alone is going to win for us.{NOTE:早川さん一人でも勝Xか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.{NOTE:信じられないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:44.42,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It that the runner-up team?{NOTE:こんなチームは準優勝したなんて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:46.80,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Where's your energy from yesterday's party, Cassie?{NOTE:パーティーの元気はどこ行ったのよ、キャシー？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:06:00.15,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,Good! Show them your Japanese fighting spirit!{NOTE:いいぞ！XXX見せてやれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.61,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,That's great support.{NOTE:すごいよ、応援ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:03.44,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,We must not let them down.{NOTE:完全はりきってなくちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.15,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Okay, stay focused!{NOTE:さ、しまってきましょう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:05.99,Default,(unknown),0,0,0,,Yeah!{NOTE:おう！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.78,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Ready or not, here I go!{NOTE:さ、やっとるぜ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.67,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Let's keep this up in the second set.{NOTE:第二セットXXXできましょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.88,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Piece of cake. Volleyball\Nis way easier than boy hunting.{NOTE:ちょろい、ちょろい。バレーはボーイハント見たいに簡単なものやあらへんで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.75,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We'll land straight victory.{NOTE:(XX・出来上がりも)ストレートで勝って見せるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:44.69,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,Something's up. It's going too well.{NOTE:XXXない。これで勝つんじゃ話が上手すぎるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.78,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Here it is, my chance ball!{NOTE:ほら来た、チャンスボールよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.00,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,They're good.{NOTE:さすがだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.25,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,An ordinary team would break under such score difference in the first set.{NOTE:普通のチームなら第一セットの大差で終わってるもんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.26,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,But they continue to play at their pace.{NOTE:彼女はあくまでマイペース。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.59,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,They're calm like the Hudson River.{NOTE:ハドソンの流れのように悠々たるもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:12.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}Hudson River - a river flowing through New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.31,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,It's just as I feared.{NOTE:恐ろしかった時は来た。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.60,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,Now they're going to show what they really can.{NOTE:これがアメリカチームのXX力のね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It was just a fluke.{NOTE:紛れ、紛れ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.19,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Let's give as good as we get.{NOTE:(XXX・代わりには鼻を明かして)ましょう。\\N}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:36.16,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Damn. Dribble.{NOTE:しまった。ドリブル。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.16,0:07:39.20,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori must be tired bad that she commenced foul play.{NOTE:みどりがドリブルする何て疲れたのかしら？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Not just Midori. Everyone's tired.{NOTE:疲れてるのはみどりだけじゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.34,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,No good. They tired us out.{NOTE:行けない。敵はXXみて全員飛ばしすぎたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Cassie's still smiling.{NOTE:キャシーは未だ笑っている。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:53.18,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Even though we are doing our best…{NOTE:私達が力を出し尽くしてるのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.10,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,…she is still so composed.{NOTE:未だ彼女は悠々たっぷりだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:03.02,Alternative,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Even a preschooler could accept that.{NOTE:こんな棒球小学生でも受けられる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.03,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got, Japanese team?{NOTE:日本人ならXXX！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.83,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,We're doing what we can.{NOTE:そんな。こっちだって一所懸命にやってるのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.29,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Don't make it more miserable.{NOTE:良い気のXXXじゃないか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.84,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Time to get serious. If the enemy plays at their pace, so will we.{NOTE:もう後はない。敵がマイペースなら、私だって私のペースで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Kozue!{NOTE:こずえ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:32.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Attack!{NOTE:アタック！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:39.51,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Beaten again.{NOTE:又遣られた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.94,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,As long as Cassie's smiling we have no chance to win.{NOTE:キャシーのあの笑いが消えないうちは勝ち目がないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.66,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,One more point. We need to get that point.{NOTE:あと一点。一点がXX取れない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.32,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,If we lose here, it's game over.{NOTE:(XX・ジュース)になったらおしまいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.89,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,Great, Japanese team!{NOTE:いいぞ日本チーム！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.15,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,It was splendid, Kozue.{NOTE:お見事こずえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:31.19,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,We were very lucky.\NWe won thanks to that last point.{NOTE:(XX・小回り)のXXXみたい。XXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.69,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,It's great that we beat the favorites at the first match.{NOTE:来世に夕食をXX下しなんて幸先いいわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.91,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But I don't understand Cassie's team.{NOTE:だけど分からないわキャシー達ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:39.62,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,They were smiling until the very end.{NOTE:さいごのさいごまで(XX・にこり)なんてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.58,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah?{NOTE:あ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.37,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Hi.{NOTE:Hi.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:46.41,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Ayuhara-san.{NOTE:お目出度う鮎原さん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, err…{NOTE:え？あ、あの…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Thank you.{NOTE:お陰様で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:52.46,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,We lost but it was a lot of fun.{NOTE:私達負けたけどとても楽しかったです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh? Fun?{NOTE:え？楽しかった？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.22,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,Yes. Volleyball is wonderful.{NOTE:Yes.バレー素晴らしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.22,0:10:02.35,Default,Cassie,0,0,0,,We are very happy to have played such a fun game with you all.{NOTE:こんなに楽しいゲームを皆さんと一緒にプレイできて私達とてもとてもハッピーです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.66,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,They're much more easy-going than us.{NOTE:所か、あれXXX変わるよなぁ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:23.70,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it,\Nvolleyball ought to be fun, right?{NOTE:そう言えばバレーって楽しいものだったね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.08,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I feel like an idiot for noticing it just now.{NOTE:馬鹿みたい今頃それに気づくなんてさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:29.25,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's no surprise. We forgot it in the middle of our special training.{NOTE:無理もないわ。特訓、特訓てしごかれたんですもの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.71,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But if we continue like this, we will end up in the finals without any problems.{NOTE:でもこの調子なら後は決勝までトントン拍子で行くわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.92,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,Let's see… our next match is with Korea, huh.{NOTE:えっと次の相手は韓国か。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.47,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Hey, the coach called us over. The Soviet team is playing now.{NOTE:ね、コーチが呼んでるわ。今ソ連チームが戦ってるの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.09,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,We're to study their style.{NOTE:XXXために是非見ろって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,The Soviets?{NOTE:ソ連チーム？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:44.60,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,What for? They're playing against some debuting team from Kenya.{NOTE:なんで相手は初出場のケニアチームじゃないの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, that team without any substitute players?{NOTE:あ、あの補欠なしの六人だけの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:50.23,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Which means Shellenina's going to go easy on them, for sure.{NOTE:それじゃ、シェレーニナはきっと調子を落としてるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:52.36,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Actually, it's on the contrary.{NOTE:ところがそれがあべこべなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:53.27,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Eh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.40,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Looks like Kenyan team puts them under pressure.{NOTE:あべこべにケニアチームが押しXXなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.40,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,What?{NOTE:何ですって？}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:02.28,Default,Ootsuki,0,0,0,,Anyway, Manumba, one of their players, is particularly outstanding.{NOTE:とにかくマヌンバって選手がとってもすごいだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.96,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,Awesome jump.{NOTE:すごいジャンプよね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:11.08,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Her arm power is great too.{NOTE:腕の力だってすごいわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:14.84,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I'd say even Olympic players can't do such a drive serve.{NOTE:あんなドライブサーブオリンピックの選手だってそうやって行っちゃうってないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.80,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,But she plays so inaccurately.{NOTE:それにしても濃厚すぎるな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,One should aim more precisely during serving.{NOTE:サーブもっと狙い撃ちしなくっちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:39.19,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Shellenina's still retains her cross toss.{NOTE:シェレーニナ未だ十字トスを出さないわね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:40.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She's saving it until the end.{NOTE:取っときなのよ、きっと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.99,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I'd like to see your famous killer spike soon, Borchinskaya-san.{NOTE:早くその殺人スパイク見せてほしいわ。ボルチンスカヤさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.49,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She aimed at the edge.{NOTE:端を狙われた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:52.42,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– She's fast!\N– Like a raging bull.{NOTE:—早い。\\N—まるで氈鹿よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.63,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She has no technique, but she sure has power.{NOTE:テクニックでは勘違いだけど、それを馬力でカバーしてるのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:58.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's not just power. It's her spirit. The fight.{NOTE:馬力だけじゃないわ。調子よ。ファイトよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.43,0:12:04.05,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.44,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Wow, not even Shellenina could receive that.{NOTE:ま。あのシェレーニナ受けられない何て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.02,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,I heard people call her "The Black Whirlwind".{NOTE:Xさきで言ってたわ。黒い旋風だって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,"The Black Whirlwind"?{NOTE:黒い旋風？}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:24.24,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We won the first game and eased up. But we still don't know what opponents we've yet to face.{NOTE:XX良い気になって私達。でもこれから先またどんな敵が現れるか分からないわ。}
Comment: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:32.58,Default,Chapter,0,0,0,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.34,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,They might actually win.{NOTE:まごまごずっと逆転やで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:43.09,Default,Sanjou,0,0,0,,She strikes well. It is reckless though.{NOTE:よく打つわね。ガムシャラな攻撃だけど。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Ah, Kozue, look at that.{NOTE:あ、こずえ、見て。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's the cross toss!{NOTE:十字トス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.77,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The cross toss.{NOTE:十字トス。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,The killer spike comes right after.{NOTE:次は殺人スパイクは出るわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.61,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,That's it. That's her killer spike!{NOTE:出た。あれが殺人スパイクなのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Sh-She received it!{NOTE:う、受けた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But something's wrong with Manumba-san.{NOTE:でも変よ、マヌンバさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She's hurt.{NOTE:怪我したんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:21.17,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She received that spike, but it fell so bad that she injured her leg.{NOTE:殺人スパイクはXXしたけど無理XX足をくじいたのね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:23.92,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,So what are they going to do?\NThe Kenyan team has no substitutes.{NOTE:じゃどうするの？ケニアチームには補欠はいないのに。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:26.30,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She's right.{NOTE:そうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:30.22,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Their country is poor and they could afford bringing only six players.{NOTE:XXX国だからあの人達たった六人でXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.72,Default,Kenia,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, no!{NOTE:No, no!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:34.06,Default,Kenia,0,0,0,,No! Oh, no!{NOTE:No! Oh, no!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.77,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,She doesn't want to leave the court.{NOTE:退場しなくて頑張ってるのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:37.23,Default,Kenia,0,0,0,,No!{NOTE:No!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:38.19,Default,Kenia,0,0,0,,No!{NOTE:No!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.57,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She wants to keep playing like this…?{NOTE:あのまま試合を続けるつもりよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:49.32,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah…{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.54,Default,Kenia,0,0,0,,Nchi yangu Kenya!{NOTE:Nchi yangu Kenya!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.00,Default,Kenia,0,0,0,,Nchi yangu Kenya!{NOTE:Nchi yangu Kenya!}
