Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:37.52,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:45.77,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,You all saw the game, didn't you?{NOTE:皆今の試合を見ただろうな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We did.{NOTE:見ました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:51.95,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Even though Kenya lost to the Soviets, they received warm applause.{NOTE:ケニアはソ連チームに溺れても満場の拍手を歩いた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.62,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,How did you view Manumba crawling on the court?{NOTE:コート這うマヌンバ選手をお前達はどう見た？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:59.37,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Did you think it was ugly?{NOTE:醜いと思ったか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:00.41,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Or…?{NOTE:それとも？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.21,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,I thought it was beautiful.{NOTE:美しいと思いました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.67,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,I see. Why?{NOTE:うん。なぜだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:08.96,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Well, that is because she tried to do her best despite being in such sorry situation.{NOTE:はい。それは彼女が泣く条件の中でベストを尽くそうとしたからです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:10.01,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Very well.{NOTE:よかろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.80,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,No matter the situation, one needs to do their utmost.{NOTE:どんな条件のもとでも全力を出し尽くす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.97,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,That posture in itself is beautiful.{NOTE:その姿こそ美しい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.06,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Let me ask another question.{NOTE:では改めて聞く。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:20.22,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Can you say your first match was beautiful?{NOTE:お前たち第一線で美しかったか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.90,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,First you were too tense.{NOTE:XXX調子XXXこのXXXお前たち。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:29.19,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Then you gave in to the crowd's taunts.\NThat posture cannot be called beautiful!{NOTE:応援の声にすらは心を満たしたお前たちが美しいはずはない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.57,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,That's all.{NOTE:それ以上。相手言わん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:37.70,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Seeing Manumba's fight was worth more than a hundred of my lectures.{NOTE:俺の100の説教よりマヌンバ選手の風船を見た方が効果があったろうからな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.58,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,The next match is Korea.{NOTE:第２選は韓国だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:44.25,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,This time you better do your best.{NOTE:その時こそお前たちのベストを尽くせ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:45.00,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,– Yes sir.\N– Yes sir.{NOTE:—はい。\\N—はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.28,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,That's bad.{NOTE:行けない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.79,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,If we keep playing like this, we won't win.{NOTE:この試合XXXいつまでも勝負がつかないわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.50,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We have to come up with something.{NOTE:何とかして切り抜けなくちゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:14.38,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Midori!{NOTE:みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:21.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Machine gun-like attack.{NOTE:機関銃攻撃。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:24.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Having Sanjou-san switch attack with Kakinouchi-san should earn us some points.{NOTE:三条さんが打ち方を見せて垣之内さんがXXこのペースでポイントを稼がなきゃ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.73,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,But Captain Sai doesn't seem to be concerned.{NOTE:でもキャプテンサイは動じていない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:32.27,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We can't let our guard down.\NCaptain Sai looks like she's up to something.{NOTE:油断は禁物。あのサイと言うキャプテンは何かやりそうだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.87,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Looks like we're in tough spot.{NOTE:ここは今のところ合格だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.41,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,We need to destroy their balance somehow.{NOTE:このバランスをXXX。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:56.34,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,That was Sai's bullet spike.{NOTE:あれが…サイの弾丸スパイクだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:19:01.01,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,She accepts the tossed ball with impetus and slams it just above the net.{NOTE:トスと見せかけたボールのそれも上がりXXXネットぎりぎりを狙う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:04.93,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's unlike Borchinskaya-san's cannon-like and Sanjou-san's machine gun-like attack.{NOTE:ボルチンスカヤの大砲とも三条さん達の機関銃とも違う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.77,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's like a rapid-fire gun.{NOTE:まるで速射砲みたいなバイクだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:11.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah!{NOTE:あ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.28,Default,Kakinouchi,0,0,0,,She did it!{NOTE:遣られた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.66,Default,Arai,0,0,0,,They're no easy opponents.{NOTE:これはXXXにXXXなチームよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.95,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,The first set is a complete defeat.{NOTE:第一セットは完敗だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:34.67,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Sai is the central figure in the Korean team.{NOTE:敵のXXXはサイさんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:37.25,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,We have to set her off somehow.{NOTE:なんとかあの人さえ崩すことができれば。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.42,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Ah, aim for their captain.{NOTE:あ、キャプテンを狙って。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:41.43,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Got it.{NOTE:よかい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.22,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,"Aim for their captain"…{NOTE:「キャプテンを狙って」。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.19,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.{NOTE:全力を尽くすわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.06,Alternative,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Look at me, Coach Inokuma.{NOTE:見せてください猪野熊コーチ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:05.83,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Excellent, Midori!{NOTE:すごい、みどり！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.45,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Your curve ball has surprised Sai-san.{NOTE:あなたの変化球サーブでサイさんをかき回すのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.14,Alternative,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Good. The second set is ours.{NOTE:よし。先ず第二セットはいただきだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,It's just like I thought.{NOTE:やっぱり思ったとおりだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.16,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Sai-san is tired and started to lose control.{NOTE:疲れたサイさんがコントロールを満たし始めたわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.56,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,– Kozue!\N– Got it!{NOTE:—こずえ！\\N—はい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:17.61,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,Attack!{NOTE:アタック！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:21.98,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,Seems they got used to\Nthe atmosphere on the court.{NOTE:どうやらコートにも雰囲気にも慣れてきた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:23.90,Default,Inokuma,0,0,0,,That's good.{NOTE:これでいい。これで。}
